OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775772667
OL,3,C'No evidence' to support criminal
OL,4,Callegation linked to Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cprobe
OL,7,FThere is no evidence to support an
OL,8,Fallegation of criminal wrongdoing made
OL,9,Fabout a police officer involved in the
OL,10,FPSNI investigation into the murder of
OL,11,Fshowjumper Katie Simpson, Police
OL,12,FOmbudsman investigators have said.
OL,14,FThe complaint centred on the initial
OL,15,Fdecision by police not to treat Ms
OL,16,FSimpson's death as suspicious and
OL,17,Falleged the officer had conflicts of
OL,18,Finterest which influenced that
OL,19,Fdecision-making.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
