FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775772667
OL,3,C'No evidence' to support criminal
OL,4,Callegation linked to Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cprobe
OL,7,FMs Simpson, 21, from Tynan, Co Armagh,
OL,8,Fdied in Altnagelvin Area Hospital
OL,9,Falmost a week after an incident in
OL,10,FGortnessy Meadows, Lettershandoney, on
OL,11,FAugust 3 2020.
OL,13,FPolice originally thought she had
OL,14,Ftaken her own life.
OL,16,FIt was not until the following year
OL,17,Fthat Jonathan Creswell, the partner of
OL,18,FMs Simpson's sister, was arrested on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of murder.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775772667
OL,3,C'No evidence' to support criminal
OL,4,Callegation linked to Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cprobe
OL,7,FThe trial of Creswell, 36, for the
OL,8,Fmurder of Ms Simpson ended in April
OL,9,Ffollowing his sudden death in 2024.
OL,11,FThe report from the Police Ombudsman
OL,12,Fsaid inquiries, including witness
OL,13,Finterviews and examinations of
OL,14,Finvestigative material, phone and
OL,15,Femail records, found no evidence of
OL,16,Fany personal connections between the
OL,17,Fpolice officer and other named parties.
OL,19,FThe case has now been closed.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNI NewsCClean Feed FThis Day
FL,448,440,140,120,000,100
PN,44704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775772667
OL,3,C'No evidence' to support criminal
OL,4,Callegation linked to Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cprobe
OL,7,FThe office of the ombudsman said the
OL,8,Ffindings of its investigation into how
OL,9,Fthe PSNI responded to Ms Simpson's
OL,10,Fdeath were reported to her family in
OL,11,FNovember 2024.
OL,13,FHowever, it said it had been unable to
OL,14,Fshare details of a specific element of
OL,15,Fthe original investigation relating to
OL,16,Fthe same police officer because of the
OL,17,Flinked complaint.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/9
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
