PN,44705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775772667
OL,3,C'No evidence' to support criminal
OL,4,Callegation linked to Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cprobe
OL,7,FThe ombudsman said this was to
OL,8,F"maintain the integrity of the
OL,9,Finvestigation and to ensure fairness
OL,10,Ffor the police officer involved".
OL,12,FThe Simpson family have now been
OL,13,Finformed that the Police Ombudsman
OL,14,Fmade no recommendations to the PSNI in
OL,15,Frespect of the police officer as part
OL,16,Fof its original investigation, and it
OL,17,Fhas found no evidence of criminal
OL,18,Fwrongdoing in its subsequent
OL,19,Finvestigation.
OL,26,@pD@AOUrD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/9
