PN,44706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775772667
OL,3,C'No evidence' to support criminal
OL,4,Callegation linked to Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cprobe
OL,7,FTwo further complaints made to the
OL,8,FPolice Ombudsman and linked to the
OL,9,Fmurder of Ms Simpson are now at an
OL,10,Fadvanced stage.
OL,12,FIn the November 2024 report, the
OL,13,Fombudsman concluded the initial police
OL,14,Finvestigation into the death of the
OL,15,Fshowjumper was "flawed" and "failed
OL,16,Fthe Simpson family".
OL,26,@wD@POUwD@WO]wD@]OUxD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/9
