OL,3,C'No evidence' to support criminal
OL,4,Callegation linked to Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cprobe
OL,7,FThat report concluded the police
OL,8,Finvestigation was hindered by the
OL,9,Fmisleading working assumption adopted
OL,10,Fby a number of officers that her
OL,11,Finjuries were self-inflicted.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G7/9
