OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F447A1775772667
OL,3,C'No evidence' to support criminal
OL,4,Callegation linked to Katie Simpson
OL,5,Cprobe
OL,7,FPSNI Assistant Chief Constable Davy
OL,8,FBeck said: "We note today's
OL,9,Fannouncement from the Police Ombudsman
OL,10,Ffor Northern Ireland (PONI), which
OL,11,Fstates that no evidence was found to
OL,12,Fsupport an allegation of criminal
OL,13,Fwrongdoing, made about a police
OL,14,Fofficer involved in the PSNI
OL,15,Finvestigation into the murder of Katie
OL,16,FSimpson.
OL,18,F"We remain committed to learning from
OL,19,Fthis case and will continue to co-
OL,20,Foperate fully with PONI in relation to
OL,21,Fany complaint."
OL,26,@pD@LOUzD@AOU}D@OO]
